{"tid":1211293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家聽我講！警察係無辜架！佢哋聽Order做野 無得反抗","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:23:26.000Z","uid":259536,"like":58,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d360588884a82a7eef37bafce8c423380060e3ee","tid":1211293,"uid":259536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"我有朋友係警察 佢話佢哋聽Order做野，無得揀，一野射落條友個頭都無計 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個士兵的律師辯護道:「這些士兵是執行命令的人，他們根本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有選擇的權利</span></span>，誰在這個崗位上都得這麼做&hellip;&hellip;」但是律師的辯護意見沒有被法官採納。法官西奧多&middot;賽德爾在解釋判決時說:「這個世界在法律之外，還有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">良知</span></span>這個東西。當法律和良知衝突的時候，良知才是最高的行為準則。尊重生命，是一個放之四海而皆準的原則。不執行上級命令是有罪的，但打不準是無罪的。作為一個心智健全的人，此時此刻，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你有『把槍口抬高一厘米</span></span>』的權利，這是你應主動承擔的良心義務。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DNZqQT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DNZqQT.gif&h=04032df8&s={SIZE}\" />[<br />\n咪撚再話警犬無辜 被逼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">良知</span></span>都無值得你和理非？<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/om5kqmo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Fom5kqmo.html&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=2ced5a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/om5kqmo.html</a>"},{"pid":"85486e7c7668df49a0f6512ea710b7b3dbae5e67","tid":1211293,"uid":245810,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌你老母，一定要射中？訓撚醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475cdeb805a9aa7b5dd932a736a6d35dcbf72c1a","tid":1211293,"uid":259536,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"警犬無辜的 佢老母